Package de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.syntax

Class Summary
LexemeProperty LexemeProperty is a class representing the central node of the SubcategorizationFrame.
SubcategorizationFrame SubcategorizationFrame is a class representing one syntactic construction.
SubcategorizationFrameSet SubcategorizationFrameSet is a class representing a set of syntactic constructions, represented by SubcatFrameSetElement instances.
SubcatFrameSetElement SubcatFrameSetElement is a class representing a syntactic construction.
SynArgMap The SynArgMap is a class representing the relationship that maps various SyntacticArgument instances of the same SubcategorizationFrameSet instance.
Therefore, every SynArgMap instance contains exactly two syntactic arguments which are in a relationship.
SyntacticArgument SyntacticArgument is a class representing an argument of a given SubcategorizationFrame instance.
SyntacticBehaviour SyntacticBehaviour is a class representing one of the possible behaviours of a lexeme.
